originalText.text: My overall experience was excellent!! Staff was pleasant, helpful and was able to quickly find an opening to see the dentist. As a patient that was told by another dentist, that I needed my 12 fillings replaced even though I had no pain or symptms, so I went to Dr. Eyckmans for a second opinion,  which was the best thing I did. He was professional, honest, transparent, and it ended being that I did not need any fillings replaced. He is an excellent dentist and I strongly recommend him.

originalText.text: I've been a patient of Dr. Eyckmans for over 20 years. He has consistently provided me and my family with excellent care. Both he and his staff are caring, warm and wonderful communicators. The office is clean, comfortable, and welcoming. I wholeheartedly recommend his services to anyone who is looking for long term dentist. Thank you Dr. Eyckmans for giving me my smile once again.
